title: Pack of C Programs
description:
This contains a pack of C programming books,
 some of them are in pdf format and some of them are in EPUB format.

It also contains some sample c programs.
It also contains a EPUB application to read epub files.
It also contains Algorithm Books.

PDF Books are:-
               1.Thomas H.Cormen,Charles E.Leiserson,Ronald L.Rivest,Clifford Stein-Introduction to algorithms,3rd edition.
               2.The c book.
	       3.Robert Sedgewick,Philippe Flajolet - An Introduction to the Analysis of Algorithms,2nd Edition.
	       4.The_c_book.
               5.Kernighan,Ritchie - The C Programming Language, 2nd edition.
 	       6.Expert C programming.
	       7.C_Programming_A_Modern_Approach_2nd_Edition_K_N_King.
    	       8.C book 1.
      	       9.Algorithms_in_a_Nutshell_George_T_Heineman_Gary_Pollice_Stanley_Selkow.
	      10.Advanced C Programming.

EPUB Files are:-
		1.Understanding and Using C Pointers.
		2.Secure Programming Cookbook for C and C++.
		3.Practical C Programming.
		4.C_Plus_Plus_All_in_one_Desk_Reference_For_Dummies_2nd_edition_John_Paul_Mueller.
		5.C in a Nutshell.

And a EPUB Application, for viewing Epub files.
    		Epub Application is portable, When ever you need it on other device just copy and paste the whole folder.


Thank You.
